{
  "chapter": 67,
  "chapter_summary": "本章\"自取其辱\"分三条线索展开。其一，阿飞发现被林仙儿欺骗后精神崩溃，上官金虹趁机以言语刺激和金钱美色诱惑，将阿飞收为己用。上官金虹先将阿飞的剑插入泥土羞辱他，再以\"为那种女人而死连狗都不如\"的话激将，最后安排七位美女和一箱珠宝引诱阿飞堕落。阿飞在绝望中选择借酒浇愁，彻底沦为上官金虹的工具。其二，龙啸云为攀附权势，带儿子龙小云向上官金虹求结拜。上官金虹百般刁难——不沾酒、不喝茶、只喝水且\"现在不渴\"，处处彰显高人一等的控制欲。龙小云年少老成，应对得体，反令上官金虹感叹\"只可惜他不是我的儿子\"。其三，上官金虹借宴席当众羞辱碧华轩少主西门玉，细数其早餐细节后以\"剖开肚子瞧瞧\"相威胁，最终以筷子封穴制服西门玉，尽显其令出如山的绝对权威。全章展现上官金虹操纵人心、碾压众人的恐怖手段。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我是全心全意地对你，你现在总该相信了吧。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这是你的剑！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若想死，很容易！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你现在若死了，绝没有人会为你悲哀，更没有人会觉得可惜，不出三天，你的尸体就会像野狗般腐烂在阴沟里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "因为一个人若为了那种女人而死，简直连狗都不如。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你想杀我？是不是？为什么还不出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若想去杀她，我也绝不阻拦你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "难道你现在已连杀人的胆子都没有了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我也知道你现在活着比死困难得多，你现在若死了，就是逃避，我想你绝不是这样的懦夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "何况，你答应我的事，现在还没有做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若还有勇气活下去，现在就跟着我走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "挺起胸膛来，走进去，莫要让人瞧着恶心。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看，世上美丽的女人并不止她一个，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你只要有这么样一口箱子，至少也可以买到一百个少女的心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nu_qun",
      "speaker_name": "少女们",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我们的心已经是他的了，用不着再买。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看，会说甜言蜜语也不只她一个，这本是女人天生就会说的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nu_qun",
      "speaker_name": "少女们",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我们说的是真话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真就是假，假就是真，真真假假，本不必太认真。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你还想死么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "死？谁想死？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "好，只要你活下去，这些全都是你的！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明天一定也是好天气……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "金钱帮属下",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将阿飞带到这里来，要他杀两个穿紫红衣裳的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "大哥的隆情厚意，实令做兄弟的永生难忘，来，兄弟敬大哥一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我从不沾酒。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "既然如此，老伯就以茶代酒如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "我也不喝茶。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "大哥平日喝的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "只喝水？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "水能清心，只喝水的人，心绝不会乱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这是清水。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "我只有渴的时候才喝水，现在我不渴。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "既然如此，小侄就替老伯喝一杯如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "你倒的，你喝。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "古人歃血为盟，以示高义，老伯与家父都是通达之士，自然不必如此看重形式，但香烛之礼却总是不可少的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "香烛又有什么用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "祀天地，祭鬼神。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "鬼神不来祭我，我为何要祭他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错，像老伯这样的盖世英雄，鬼神必也十分相敬。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "我不敬他，他为何要敬我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "那么，老伯的意思……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "是令尊要和我结拜，还是你？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "当然是家父。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "text": "那么你就站到一边去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_jr",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "犬子无礼，大哥千万莫要见怪。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "这样的儿子，怎能说是犬子？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "只可惜他不是我的儿子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_mei_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "浓眉大汉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "令已传去，只不过……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_nong_mei_da_han",
      "text": "只不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_mei_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "浓眉大汉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "看来他已醉了，醉得很厉害。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_nong_mei_da_han",
      "text": "用冷水泼，若泼不醒，就用尿。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_mei_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "浓眉大汉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "大哥莫非在等人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "谁配要我等？",
      "tone": "傲慢",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "既然人都已到了，大哥为何还不……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "贵庚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "虚长五十一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你比我大，是否我该叫你一声大哥才对？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "年无长幼，能者为师，大哥千万莫折煞小弟。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "既然我是大哥，你就该听我的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "好，坐下来喝酒……先敬这些朋友一杯。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒菜已叫来，不吃就是浪费，我最恨浪费，各位请。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这鱼还新鲜，大哥为何不也尝一些？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我饿的时候才吃，现在我不饿。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不饿的时候吃，也是浪费。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "这酒菜中有毒！",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "怎会有毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "既然无毒，你为何不吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "在下不饿，不敢浪费帮主的酒菜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "真的不饿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "真……真的。",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "浪费还可原谅，说谎却不可恕，你明白么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这种小事，在下又何必说谎。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "说谎就是说谎，大事小事全都一样。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不饿就是不饿。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "现在已过了午饭时候，你怎会不饿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "也许在下吃的早点还未消化。",
      "tone": "辩解",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "你早点是在城南'奎元馆'吃的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "你一个人要了一碗麻油鸡，一碗爆鳝鱼面，外带一笼肉包，鸡吃了两块，面你只吃了半碗，肉包吃了七个，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "想不到帮主将在下的一举一动都调查得如此仔细。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "你吃的这些东西既然还未消化，想必还留在肚子里，是么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "想必还在的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "text": "好，剖开他的肚子瞧瞧，还在不在？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yu",
      "speaker_name": "西门玉",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "帮主莫非是在开玩笑？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 67,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    }
